criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Have signed an approved informed consent form for the stud;

          -  Histologically confirmed rectal adenocarcinoma low (cT2-4N0-2M0) or mid rectum
             (сТ2-T4N1-2M0);

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  rectal cancer recurrence;

          -  Primary-multiple tumours of other localizations;

          -  pelvis radiotherapy in anamnesis;

          -  pregnancy, breastfeeding;

          -  distant metastasis;

          -  ECOG score 3-4
